{"type":null,"faqId":48069,"title":"华为钱包","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>                </span><span class=\"s1\"> 惠生活</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"惠生活\"XE \"优惠信息\"XE \"充话费\"XE \"电影票\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178055\" style=\"width:0.24305555in;height:0.1875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“华为钱包”，在“惠生活”页签，您可以进行理财、话费充值、手机预购等，给手机充值还能享受更多优惠。</span><a name=\"_task_hw_wallet-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">我的钱包</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"华为钱包\"XE \"信用卡\"XE \"银行卡\"XE \"买应用\"XE \"买主题\"XE \"买游戏\"XE \"买壁纸\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>使用华为钱包可以快捷安全地购买您喜欢的应用、虚拟游戏道具、主题和壁纸等娱乐内容。使用钱包前，请先按照屏幕提示注册或登录一个华为帐号。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178056\" style=\"width:0.24305555in;height:0.1875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“华为钱包”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“我的钱包”页签，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“我的银行卡 &gt; 关联银行卡”，按照屏幕提示完成银行卡的关联。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“设置 &gt; 安全设置”，设置支付密码、手势密码和安保问题，保护您的帐号安全。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3655","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598109000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":127,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}